name: Pushin' 'Em Out
description:
A clicker game made in 48 hours for the Brains Eden 2016 game jam. This game is designed for gyroscopic on android tablets. (There may be some bugs)

Repopulate the earth by any means neccessary or doom the human race to extinction.

Paul Palmer (https://paulsiclegames.wordpress.com/) - Programming, design, writing
Sean Logue (Seanpl.portfoliobox.net) - Programming, design
Oliver Knight (http://oliknight95.wix.com/oliverkportfolio) - Design, writing
Callum Wilkins - Design, art
